item.title: Plastic Lines - Wake Me Up
item.description: Just Am, F, C, G. This video has the play-along with a simpler strum pattern at the original tempo. Use this link to access the practice video for the syncopated strum (https://youtu.be/CPlUsgAAWA8). Use this link to access the play-along with the syncopated strum at a slower place (https://youtu.be/Hz1tPr_gLNc). Use this link to access the play-along with the syncopated strum at the original speed (https://youtu.be/7tNG1J2ybgo).
